                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.62119/98: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Germany</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dresel</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-11-26T19:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 26, 1921—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1547. Your 806, November 23, 4 p.m.</p>
                <p>Executive Proclamation of Peace with Germany reads in part as follows “The war
                    between the United States and Germany terminated on July 2, 1921.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
